    "Synchronous and async clients for ESIOS API access",
    "Retrieve electricity market indicators (prices, generation, demand)",
    "Download archives including I90 settlement files",
    "Intelligent parquet-based caching for performance",
    "Multi-geography indicator support with automatic pivoting",
    "Pandas DataFrame integration for data analysis",
    "CLI tool for quick data access and exploration",
    "Offline catalog of 600+ indicators and 150+ archives"
